            },
            "description": "Teste gRPC OrderService.CreateOrder.\nVérifie les types Protobuf : repeated OrderItem, float total.\nVérifie le déclenchement Kafka (event ORDER_CREATED).\n\nCommande grpcurl directe :\ngrpcurl -plaintext -import-path ./proto -proto order.proto \\\n  -d '{\"customer_id\":\"client-grpc\",\"items\":[{\"product_id\":\"p3\",\"product_name\":\"Casque Audio Z\",\"quantity\":1,\"unit_price\":99.99}]}' \\\n  localhost:50052 order.OrderService/CreateOrder"
          }
